    description:
      "Nibbi Clothing is a community-driven tennis & lifestyle clothing brand – inspired by tennis’ culture, aesthetics, and history. We are also a “sports club” where customers have the opportunity to participate in tournaments, trainings and events. Our goal and vision are to spread the lifestyle associated with tennis, both off and on the court.Nibbi clothing is strongly inspired by the aesthetics and colors of tennis, with sportswear and cotton garments. The sportswear consists of full tennis sets with shorts, piques, t-shirts, socks, caps, and cushions. All the cotton garments are hand-printed by us in Oslo. This makes it possible for us to create our own prints and motives, using a technique called screen printing. We release several small collections with unique prints and colors for Nibbi, in addition to collaborations with some selected partners.We want to be a brand that inspires people to get out on the court by bringing out the playfulness, social and sporting aspects of Tennis. Tennis is a sport that suits all levels – we are a brand for both newcomers and professional players.\n\nWe mainly sell through our online store at www.nibbiclothing.no, where we always have all the products available. Throughout the year we also have several pop-ups. We use the online store to communicate with customers through stories and unique offers for our sports club members.",
